      <h2>How to participate</h2>
      <p>If you have a hiker's account, go to the login page and login to access your information.</p>
      <p>If you don't have hiker's account yet, go to the login page and click on the "Signup" link to create a new account.</p>
      <p>With a hiker's account you can add individual hike's to your list of accomplishments. Each hike you complete will be listed in your account's hiking details.</p>
      <p>You can also read more about all the clubs and mountains that are part of the Euro Mountaineering hiking experience.</p>
      <p>Come back often to update your progress and see what new mountain adventures are available to conquer.</p>
